A small sidebar into “Crisis Fatigue” (also known as Compassion Fatigue or Secondary Traumatic Stress)
#262 Do You Lack Motivation? Procrastinate? Miss Deadlines? Fatigued? Here is why…: https://t.co/hmHYi93Mr8 via @YouTube
Tl;dr: fashionably kill your characters, and don’t fatigue your audience by drawing out many deaths
TWD hits Crisis Fatigue very early, dropping old characters and picking up new characters within just a handful of episodes, yet you still have this core set of people who appear to be immune to this

“Crisis Fatigue” is a very real thing, when too much of something bad happens, people stop reacting to it. We see this quite often in what types of stories are put out on the news (I.e. if two shooting happen, only one will be reported)
